high_descs: Head straight, turn left, head to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn left, bring the mug to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Take the chilled mug back to the coffee machine to the right.
Put the chilled mug back on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Head towards the counter, then turn left and go to the coffee maker.
Pick up the coffee mug from the coffee maker.
Turn left and head towards the refrigerator.
Put the coffee mug in the refrigerator for a few seconds and then pull it back out.
Turn around and head to the coffee maker.
Put the coffee mug on to the coffee maker tray.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee mug on to the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk to the counter, turn left, and stop in front of the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn to the left and stop in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the coffee mug inside, close the door, wait a few seconds, take the coffee mug out of the fridge.
Turn to the right and walk back to the coffee maker.
Place the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To chill a mug for coffee.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter in front of the coffee maker.
Pick up the coffee cup from the coffee maker.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the coffee cup inside the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the coffee maker.
Put the coffee cup on to the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled coffee cup into the coffee maker.
